{"tid":1427082,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］三毛即將攻陷連登！！請大家注意","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:43:37.000Z","uid":203845,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b4255f1bc99a6eb80e891ad8e051534fb56259c9","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"唔知大家覺唔覺得，呢排嘅連登好亂<br />\n好似有人帶緊風向<br />\n令我地混亂，大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 三你個頭呀。根本冇咁多三毛</span><br />\n大家仲記唔記得雨革後期係點？<br />\n就係係咁捉鬼<br />\n而家只不過由鬼變咗三毛<br />\n個感覺唔係好熟悉咩？<br />\n<br />\n中共最叻人民鬥人民，分化<br />\n你地就係咁覺得佢地分化緊唔同立場嘅人<br />\n錯晒呀！！<br />\n你睇下連登<br />\n唔同意見就係三毛，P牌就更加冇人比人話<br />\n我好相信P牌嘅原意<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係叫大家提高警覺</span><br />\n而唔係一窩蜂鬧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設連登有10萬活躍會員<br />\n咁連登就有10萬種意見<br />\n點可以單憑人地意見唔同，就係鬼？<br />\n我地成日笑三毛嘅言論，覺得佢地廢<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但係三毛嘅可怕不在於佢帶風向</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而係在於佢地令我地草木皆兵，最後只要意見不同就會被批鬥，最終失去支持</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要杜絕三毛嘅長遠辦法<br />\n係要每個連登用戶，甚至CD-rom 都用腦<br />\n唔好人地講咩就認同<br />\n認同之前用腦諗下<br />\n問下你嘅初心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當初我地出嚟係追求民主<br />\n但係如果我地最後都變成一言堂<br />\n咁先係呢場運動嘅徹底失敗</span> <br />\n<br />\n仲有勇武嘅手足<br />\n你地嘅付出同抗爭係成場運動嘅關鍵<br />\n點解？因為你地而家代替咗警犬<br />\n成為真真正正保護香港市民嘅一群<br />\n<br />\n但係能力越大，責任越大<br />\n班狗之所以不得民心<br />\n係佢地衝動，冇禮貌，對市民做成困擾<br />\n呢排好多連登仔講嘅路西法效應<br />\n呢度亦都唔多講<br />\n<br />\n但係想講嘅係，要保護人民<br />\n首先要自律同得民心<br />\n同時所有行動必需出於保護市民先做<br />\n市民對我地可能有誤解<br />\n所以一方面文宣要加大宣傳<br />\n我地係企喺人民嘅一邊<br />\n另一方面，前線手足嘅行動<br />\n就係最好嘅宣傳<br />\n<br />\n喺而家呢個局勢，相信大家都緊張<br />\n甚至心情會好差<br />\n但係我地更加要克制<br />\n點解？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為人同狗最大嘅分別，就係唔會以情緒行先同目標導向</span><br />\n希望大家可以重整一下<br />\n重新搵返當日嘅初心<br />\n咁先係呢場運動嘅必勝秘訣<br />\n<br />\n無忘初心<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n多謝一齊行到呢度嘅各位手足"},{"pid":"10c9b701b131afbbdb19eb13976eb19b67236aad","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n認同嘅請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c1ef463d950688b31d70cffe256b1548825168","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"又或者唔認同嘅亦都希望你講下<br />\n連登係討論區，唔討論係冇任何意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd47359e18bff5b738df9c07ce159c6f02f8617","tid":1427082,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d4180c40eda401ac264382b437064c33d885921","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"準備自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186ad4316ad25ec31c473f2f9dce2686112c2bf3","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:28.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"b5ce0c9e7d27388fdb8bcaaae7f14f4a42ad77de","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"b3631ed81849048aa20475e06b0c67e6d1334bcb","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"792f990b83bdbc7985c136e50ea6b304449f8693","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"19319544ee98cf0de44acbcfee029eb472f6c256","tid":1427082,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"標題撚<br />\n標題話三毛攻陷<br />\n內文又話邊有咁多<br />\n<br />\n要起個咁既標題引人注意即係心知自己內文係廢話<br />\n勸你睇少D寫個垃圾TOPIC引人睇既YOUTUBE"},{"pid":"502a86df9754fe8eb8d71797aed36776a0f85779","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:56:50.000Z","msg":"唔該大家幫下手<br />\n認同嘅推下<br />\n因為真係好關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家係咁亂diu身邊手足<br />\n已經係好大警號"},{"pid":"c52d0634c2b77179ce1b69a22b8505b6225d2870","tid":1427082,"uid":209531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c306acfdfd674f6267a1be71e2c916fad9790acf","tid":1427082,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"雨革後期係係咁捉左膠<br />\n<br />\n但對個結局無影響喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690939fded4678f7fe49256be748bd9299dad0ea","tid":1427082,"uid":70885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05aace7039d9a28b3f419729e9de035fc9c5e1b","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19319544ee98cf0de44acbcfee029eb472f6c256","tid":1427082,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"標題撚<br />\n標題話三毛攻陷<br />\n內文又話邊有咁多<br />\n<br />\n要起個咁既標題引人注意即係心知自己內文係廢話<br />\n勸你睇少D寫個垃圾TOPIC引人睇既YOUTUBE"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:59:10.000Z","msg":"係唔係廢話。我相信大家睇得出<br />\n用標題引人注意<br />\n係除咗呢d標題其他人根本唔睇<br />\n不如我地又睇下熱門有幾多真係有用post?<br />\n大家就係圍爐，或者捉鬼<br />\n當然呢個標題係垃圾<br />\n但係我希望大家睇完<br />\n呢種標題嘅post係最後一次大家會推嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06204523b54df19b5fb33bb448a2a0889db35c5","tid":1427082,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4125ce2303ca46d0cf40313f6dbc55bb931a54e8","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c306acfdfd674f6267a1be71e2c916fad9790acf","tid":1427082,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"雨革後期係係咁捉左膠<br />\n<br />\n但對個結局無影響喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"捉左膠，我地知嗰個係邊個<br />\n大家可以調查<br />\n連登呢？而家問題嘅係，我地自己內部分化<br />\n唔解決，就死路一條"},{"pid":"06ce0320d0104d4d07447866c25394ce9261351b","tid":1427082,"uid":131122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"好多捉鬼係真<br />\n已經就黎重犯同一錯誤"},{"pid":"30cecd0c0747c22462bf7d9141daf839b8cf6214","tid":1427082,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cc0444f1c8b4ac5d94badc3be7d35aba6107c5a","tid":1427082,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb90b35a53fdfdff8e867cf1004ad4f8b97eb481","tid":1427082,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"咪再亂屌人係三毛<br />\n三毛無咁醒"},{"pid":"b64161843e1f8df200e564c7b092f16e46cc1185","tid":1427082,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594028a78154ab56dc4e6272e4d7e6162edce3f3","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"最緊要係帶腦睇連登<br />\n大家群起叫分化撚，三毛，係唔會幫到件事"},{"pid":"7ba63b5c798bb567f35f03e33806eb287fef9c4a","tid":1427082,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"愈深色個腦愈殘"},{"pid":"05052765478c17e67a847043827f621df7eb3c29","tid":1427082,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />豬之亂"},{"pid":"243fdc9b63bb048d1bff13a958f968957103c6cd","tid":1427082,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ce0320d0104d4d07447866c25394ce9261351b","tid":1427082,"uid":131122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:02:14.000Z","msg":